# ── Nullkey secrets & runtime state — NEVER commit these ────────────────────
# Your identity, keys, and contacts ARE your account. Leaking them deanonymizes
# you and your contacts. These must catch them under ANY data-dir name.
# (Note: .gitignore only treats '#' as a comment at the START of a line — never
#  put a comment after a pattern, or the pattern silently stops matching.)
data/
peer*/
tor*/
# private keys: crypto_identity.key, onion_identity.key
*.key
# any file holding a raw onion address
*.onion
# the contact book (peer onion addresses + public keys), at any depth
contacts.json
**/contacts.json
# Tor runtime state
.tor-*/
.tor-data/

# ── Python ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/

# ── C/C++ build artifacts (Phase 3) ─────────────────────────────────────────
build/
*.so
*.pyd
*.dll
*.exe
*.o
*.obj
*.lib
*.exp
*.pdb
*.egg-info/
*.dSYM/

# ── Test / tooling caches ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
.secrets.baseline

# ── OS / editor junk ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/

# ── Personal docs (not for public repo) ─────────────────────────────────────
PROGRESS.md
docs/PROGRESS.md
secure-messenger-prd.md
docs/secure-messenger-prd.md
LEARNING-PATH.md
docs/LEARNING-PATH.md
